      <title>朝鲜罕见派代表团访问伊朗，引发武器担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/north-korea-stokes-arms-concerns-by-sending-a-rare-delegation-to-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜派遣了大约五年来最高级别的代表团访问伊朗，美国担心平壤和德黑兰的武器销售助长了中东冲突和俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/north-korea-stokes-arms-concerns-by-sending-a-rare-delegation-to-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 06:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
