    <item>
      <title>Milei 的团队认为阿根廷通胀放缓速度快于经济学家调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/milei-s-team-sees-inflation-slowing-faster-than-economist-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱的经济团队认为，今年月度通胀放缓的速度比分析师预期的要快得多，这是他的顾问在试图使国家摆脱危机时做出的罕见洞察。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/milei-s-team-sees-inflation-slowing-faster-than-economist-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 04:54:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
